
Fichiers journal bookings:   (id performance.bookings)

ligne
1: bookingsV1
2: description texte de la représentation
3: id performance | nombre total de places | id show | id room
4: COMMAND | ...
...

COMMAND possibles:

BOOK   | id booking | date de la reservation | nombre de places | nom | [commentaire] | nb free seats after change
UNBOOK | id booking | date de l'annulation | nombre de places | nom | nb free seats after change
SELL   | id ticket | date de la vente | tarif | prix payé | nb seats | nb free seats after change
UNSELL | id ticket | date de l'annulation | tarif | nb seats | nb free seats after change
SETNBSEATS| total | [ libres | reserves | vendus | en cours ]

JUSQUE LA WRITE OK

SETSHOW | id show | titre (optional)
SETROOM | id room | name (optional)
SETDATE | date (dd.MM.yyyy 'at' HH:mm:ss z)
ADDPRICE | id price | action | title | prix | validity comment
DELETEPRICE | id price | action | title | prix | validity comment
UPDATEPRICE | id price | action | title | prix | validity comment


UPDATEBOOKING   | id booking | date de la reservation | nombre de places | nom | [commentaire] | nb free seats after change

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Fichier setup:  (bouboutel.setup)

ligne
1: bouboutelV1
2: COMMAND | ...
....

COMMAND possibles:

SETBACKUPDIRECTORY | path

ADDPERFORMER | id performer | signature | name | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail
ADDSHOW | id show | signature | titre | id performer
ADDROOM | id room | signature | nom | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail | default seat number
ADDPERFORMANCE | id performance | signature | date | id room | id show | nb total seats


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fichier variables statiques:  (bouboutel.statics)

performance counter
ticket counter
contact counter
show counter
booking counter
price counter

