(NOT USED)

Ficher journal setup:

ligne
1: setupV1
2: COMMAND | ...


COMMAND possibles:

SETDATADIRECTORY | path
SETBACKUPDIRECTORY | path

ADDPERFORMANCE | id performance | date | id room | total nb seats
UPDATEPERFORMANCE | id performance | date | id room | total nb seats
DELETEPERFORMANCE | id performance
ADDPERFORMER | id performer | name | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail
UPDATEPERFORMER | id performer | name | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail
DELETEPERFORMER | id performer
ADDSHOW | id show | titre | id performer
UPDATESHOW | id show | titre | id performer
DELETESHOW | id show
ADDROOM | id room | nom | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail | default seat number
UPDATEROOM | id room | nom | rue | ville | pays | phone | e-mail | default seat number
DELETEROOM | id room

